Gastrointestinal and metabolic impairments in cystic fibrosis. This article is about the peculiarities of gastrointestinal lesions, and the nature of metabolic disorders in patients with cystic fibrosis. Presented statistical data abouth the frequency of various gastrointestinal disorders in cystic fibrosis, studied the spectrum of ultrasound changes and changes in the biochemical status of patients with cystic fibrosis.